{"type":null,"faqId":12006,"title":"G620-L72  使用数据业务上网经常掉线，如何解决？","answer":"<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">请在移动网络信号较强的地方上网。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">进入“设置”界面，点击“移动网络”，勾选“始终连接数据业务”复选框。<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=33390\" /></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">向网络运营商咨询手机的接入点名称（</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';font-size:10.5pt;\">APN</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">）参数是否正确。在“移动网络”中，点击“接入点名称（</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';font-size:10.5pt;\">APN</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">）”，可以查看当前使用的接入点。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=33391\" /></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">若尝试以上方法后仍然不能解决问题，请备份重要数据后将手机恢复出厂设置，然后重新连接。</span> </span></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span>* </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"></span>&nbsp;\n</p>","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":0,"unUseful":2,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2794","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1398823976000,"seriesProductName":"G620-L72","visitedTimes":63,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"使用数据业务上网经常掉线","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}